item.title: Quick-n-Dirty Crusty Bread
item.description: Ingredients (makes 4 medium loaves) 3 cups lukewarm water ( 105 â„‰ ) 2 lbs. unbleached all-purpose flour ( weighed on a scale ) 1 tablespoon salt 1 1⁄2 tablespoons instant or active dry yeast Recipe Combine all of the ingredients in a large mixing bowl Mix by hand to make a very sticky, rough dough. Cover the bowl, and let the dough rise at room temperature for 2 hours.
